  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endlessly Gather Resources with Your Friends !</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Idle Together</strong> is a <strong>resource management and accumulation</strong> game where you can <strong>collaborate with other players</strong> to optimize your progress. Accessible to everyone, it combines the fun of idle games with <strong>unique cooperative mechanics</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build the Village of Your Dreams</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine <strong>villager management</strong> with <strong>building construction</strong> to help them improve and work more efficiently. <strong>Optimize</strong> the placement of buildings to <strong>reduce travel time</strong>, or simply create the <strong>most beautiful village possible</strong> in <strong>unique, procedurally generated worlds</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/a6a59894d8f26921ff0d784e9af90d2f.poster.avif?t=1768372964\" width=800 height=133 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/a6a59894d8f26921ff0d784e9af90d2f.webm?t=1768372964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Villagers with Human-Like Behavior</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They're <strong>lazy and not too bright</strong>… at least at first. You'll need to <strong>keep an eye on them </strong>: some will wander to the other side of the world just to gather a few berries, while others will <strong>hide in a bush</strong> just to sneak in a quick nap.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/3d67560a33686e81c1e7940c7df2a92f.poster.avif?t=1768372964\" width=800 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/3d67560a33686e81c1e7940c7df2a92f.webm?t=1768372964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/3d67560a33686e81c1e7940c7df2a92f.mp4?t=1768372964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Level Up Your Professions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each click is an opportunity to <strong>improve a profession</strong> and <strong>earn even more rewards</strong> with every action. Multiply your <strong>profitability</strong> while having fun !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/f1ad8032b101b84a171662495ef7c1b1.poster.avif?t=1768372964\" width=800 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/f1ad8032b101b84a171662495ef7c1b1.webm?t=1768372964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/f1ad8032b101b84a171662495ef7c1b1.mp4?t=1768372964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>More, More, Always More</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep accumulating <strong>more and more</strong> resources <strong>automatically</strong> or by clicking !<br>These resources are <strong>precious</strong>—they'll allow you to <strong>level up</strong>, over and over again…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/af6e77aa11672535bae7b4ffda433b45.poster.avif?t=1768372964\" width=800 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/af6e77aa11672535bae7b4ffda433b45.webm?t=1768372964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/af6e77aa11672535bae7b4ffda433b45.mp4?t=1768372964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Magical Power of Constellations</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your villagers <strong>believe in the power of the stars</strong>, and when you believe… it becomes <strong>reality</strong>.<br><strong>Build stunning constellations</strong> based on your strategy to <strong>enhance your power</strong> and <strong>control them all</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>unique system</strong> that will unlock, throughout the game, <strong>new gameplay elements</strong>, such as practical features like <strong>saving</strong> ! In this game, you will need to unlock these elements to progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/fe4407af22b5cf033ab48853ab0534cb.poster.avif?t=1768372964\" width=800 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/fe4407af22b5cf033ab48853ab0534cb.webm?t=1768372964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/fe4407af22b5cf033ab48853ab0534cb.mp4?t=1768372964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All set in a <strong>vibrant pixel art world</strong>, accompanied by <strong>relaxing music</strong>, creating a <strong>soothing atmosphere</strong> after a long day. <strong>A game designed for the whole family</strong>, perfect for a <strong>fun and relaxing time</strong> with your loved ones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Join the adventure and discover a world where <strong>strategy, cooperation, and resource management</strong> come together for a unique and endless experience !</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endlessly Gather Resources with Your Friends !</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Idle Together</strong> is a <strong>resource management and accumulation</strong> game where you can <strong>collaborate with other players</strong> to optimize your progress. Accessible to everyone, it combines the fun of idle games with <strong>unique cooperative mechanics</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build the Village of Your Dreams</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine <strong>villager management</strong> with <strong>building construction</strong> to help them improve and work more efficiently. <strong>Optimize</strong> the placement of buildings to <strong>reduce travel time</strong>, or simply create the <strong>most beautiful village possible</strong> in <strong>unique, procedurally generated worlds</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/a6a59894d8f26921ff0d784e9af90d2f.poster.avif?t=1768372964\" width=800 height=133 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/a6a59894d8f26921ff0d784e9af90d2f.webm?t=1768372964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Villagers with Human-Like Behavior</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They're <strong>lazy and not too bright</strong>… at least at first. You'll need to <strong>keep an eye on them </strong>: some will wander to the other side of the world just to gather a few berries, while others will <strong>hide in a bush</strong> just to sneak in a quick nap.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468430/extras/3